This dashboard shows a complete overview of Amazon Prime movies and TV shows data in one place. At the top, it displays key numbers like total titles, ratings, genres, directors, and the time period (1920 to 2021).

The charts help to understand the data easily:

It shows how many shows are available for different age ratings like 13+, 16+, etc.
It highlights the most popular genres such as Drama and Comedy
A world map shows which countries produce more content
A pie chart compares Movies and TV Shows (movies are more)
A graph shows how content has increased over the years

Overall, this page gives a quick and clear summary of Amazon Prime content using simple visuals.
